lemma D_last_index_compE\<^sub>1: "\<And>A Vs. \<lbrakk> A \<subseteq> set Vs; fv e \<subseteq> set Vs \<rbrakk> \<Longrightarrow> \<D> e \<lfloor>A\<rfloor> \<Longrightarrow> \<D> (compE\<^sub>1 Vs e) \<lfloor>last_index Vs ` A\<rfloor>" and "\<And>A Vs. \<lbrakk> A \<subseteq> set Vs; fvs es \<subseteq> set Vs \<rbrakk> \<Longrightarrow> \<D>s es \<lfloor>A\<rfloor> \<Longrightarrow> \<D>s (compEs\<^sub>1 Vs es) \<lfloor>last_index Vs ` A\<rfloor>"
